復香港，你我有責 </span></span>"},{"pid":"db3591b93fa9134479ff0b35189c8e701bb7c1b1","tid":2025163,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n承上<br />\n<br />\n好耐無比海綿寶carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50d9cc162750f045ba08cf4f7cd8cb4e717cc38","tid":2025163,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3591b93fa9134479ff0b35189c8e701bb7c1b1","tid":2025163,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n承上<br />\n<br />\n好耐無比海綿寶carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"佢抽我水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 推呢個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[PS4/PC] Monster Hunter World: Iceborne [419] 絕影拎完1001唔開po可恥<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2025158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2025158</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9694b8c24e9d55712b3bfa96df965546cfe5d630","tid":2025163,"uid":166126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:52:01.000Z","msg":"我睇巴哈話絢輝龍會係5月25定26號再開返，係咪真？<br />\n我上官網睇唔到有講既"},{"pid":"bf748196457618ee4a77ca27a69c7e4804b05d7b","tid":2025163,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇pc巴打可以聚魔開隻普通水妖鳥<br />\n我發現打左咁耐未打過佢啲素材所以煉金唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n@華dee<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通水妖鳥 你引怪嗰度冇得引？"},{"pid":"28dd58b51dfe642518ca37c8aa081dcd2e6a2811","tid":2025163,"uid":312592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"新手入ib 換左套冰魚龍裝<br />\n打到去轟龍迅龍已經好撚辛苦<br />\n係咪已經需要換裝<br />\n<br />\n但